places.address: H2MP+PWV Chavakkad Mahallu Juma Masjid, Palayoor - Angadi Rd, Edappully, Guruvayur, Kerala 680506

featured_reviews.review_id:
It's a great neighbourhood with a lot of history and a pleasant attitude.
The committee is regularly good developing the masjid and related places.
It's a historical masjid with a lot of great energy.
The masjid is now completely air-conditioned. It is beneficial to all people.
You must replace the masjid's electric man, as he is unfamiliar with electrical supply.
Otherwise, everything is in order. The committee is performing admirably.
